article.description: — Joel Soriano had 18 points in St. John's 85-50 win over Sacred Heart on Wednesday night.
article.headline: St. John's wins 85-50 over Sacred Heart
article.linkText: St. John's wins 85-50 over Sacred Heart
article.story: NEW YORK -- — Joel Soriano had 18 points in St. John's 85-50 win over Sacred Heart on Wednesday night. Soriano had 13 rebounds and six assists for the Red Storm (6-2). Jordan Dingle was 7 of 11 shooting (3 for 7 from 3-point range) to add 17 points. Daniss Jenkins shot 5 for 12, including 3 for 6 from beyond the arc to finish with 13 points. Nico Galette finished with 13 points, seven rebounds, five assists and two steals for the Pioneers (4-6). Kyle McGee added eight points and two steals for Sacred Heart. Raymond Espinal-Guzman also had seven points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
